ShareOverviewSummaryCharter Cable Partners, Llc has worked on eighteen contracts worth $78,935 USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2016), the organization received a total of $9,170 USD in obligations.The principal agencies it has contracted with are the Department of Veterans Affairs, Department of Justice, and Department of Defense.

